On 28 July 2016, Sergeant Reckless was posthumously awarded the [[Dickin Medal]] for her service between 1952 and 1953.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bailey |first1=Nancy |title=U.S. Marine Horse 'Sgt Reckless' Awarded Posthumous Medal Of Valor |url=http://www.inquisitr.com/3358373/u-s-marine-horse-sgt-reckless-awarded-posthumous-medal-of-valor/ |accessdate=29 July 2016 |publisher=The Inquisitr News |date=28 July 2016}}</ref>
