iller|2013}}|last=Miller|first=Joshua Rhett|title=Statue of Korean War Horse Reckless to be Unveiled at Marine museum in Virginia|url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2013/07/24/statue-korean-war-horse-reckless-to-be-unveiled-at-marine-museum-in-virginia/|publisher=Fox News|date=July 25, 2013|accessdate=27 July 2013}} * {{cite news|ref={{sfnRef|Equestrian News|2012}}|last=Staff|title=Hoofed Heroine Sgt. Reckless|url=http://theequestriannews.com/2012/11/12/hoofed-heroine-sgt-reckless/|date= November 12, 2012|publisher=The Equestrian News|accessdate=28 July 2013}} * {{cite news|ref={{sfnRef|Baltimore Sun|2013}}|last=Staff|title=Native Dancer (1950–1967)|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/sports/preakness-insider-blog/bal-horse-list-0516-native-dancer-19671129,0,3500525.photo|year=2013|publisher=The Baltimore Sun|accessdate=29 July 2013}} * {{cite news|ref={{sfnRef|Tuscaloosa News|1968}}|last=Staff|title=Sgt Reckless Dies; Heroic Marine Mare|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1817&dat=19680521&id=WHAfAAAAIBAJ&sjid=M5sEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6304,4254522|date=May 21, 1968|publisher=The Tuscaloosa News|accessdate=28 July 2013}} * {{cite web|ref={{sfnRef|Marine Corps News|2013}}|last=Staff|title=Ultimate Marine (Puller vs Butler)|url=http://marines.dodlive.mil/2013/04/10/ultimate-marine-puller-vs-butler/|date=April 10, 2013|publisher=Marine Corps News|accessdate=28 July 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731072526/http://marines.dodlive.mil/2013/04/10/ultimate-marine-puller-vs-butler/|archivedate=31 July 2013|df=}} * {{cite AV media|ref={{sfnRef|Sgt Reckless video|2010}} | date = 8 August 2010| title = Sgt Reckless&nbsp;— Korean War Horse Hero | url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YIo3ZfA9da0 | accessdate = 28 July 2013| time = 0:39–1:29, 2:19–2:45| publisher = sgtreckless.com via Marine Corps archives}} {{refend}}
